  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wherever people are hurt, or sickness is spreading, you've got to Heal The Survivors!<br><br><strong><u>Features:</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Art\" Gallery *</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lifetime Stats **</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 <span class=\"bb_strike\">REDACTED</span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 difficulties</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 backgrounds</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 crewmembers</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12 incidents</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12 tools</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12 <span class=\"bb_strike\">REDACTED</span>s</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20 skills</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >24 upgradables</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100 achievements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1000s of patients to heal</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >no subscription necessary</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >no microtransactions</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >no in app purchases</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >no paid dlc</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >no ads</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >nobody dies<br><br><i>* The term \"Art\" is doing a lot of heavy lifting here, fair warning.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>** Lifetime Stats can be reset in the Options Menu. Do NOT give your little brother your device, make him get his own.</i></p>",
